team1.name: Team Liquid
team1.description: Team Liquid is a professional esports organization founded in the Netherlands in 2000. Originally a Brood War clan, the team switched to StarCraft II during the SC2 Beta in 2010, and became one of the most successful foreign teams. On August 7, 2020, Team Liquid entered VALORANT by signing fish123.
